<% title = 'About Us' %>
<div class="about-container fade-in premium-about">
  <div class="card fade-in">
    <h1 class="about-title text-center mb-2">About Sweet Delights</h1>
    <div class="about-section fade-in">
      <img src="/images/about-banner.jpg" alt="Our Bakery" class="about-banner rounded shadow mb-2">
      <h2 class="about-heading">Our Story</h2>
      <p class="about-text">
        Sweet Delights was founded in 2010 by a group of passionate pastry chefs who wanted to bring high-quality, handcrafted desserts to dessert lovers everywhere. What started as a small bakery in a quiet neighborhood has grown into a beloved destination for those seeking exceptional sweet treats.
      </p>
      <p class="about-text">
        Our mission is simple: to create desserts that bring joy and satisfaction to our customers. We believe in using only the finest ingredients, supporting local suppliers, and crafting each item with care and attention to detail.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-section fade-in">
      <h2 class="about-heading">Our Values</h2>
      <div class="about-values-grid">
        <div class="about-value-card">
          <h3>Quality</h3>
          <p>We never compromise on the quality of our ingredients or our products. Every dessert is made to meet our high standards.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-value-card">
          <h3>Innovation</h3>
          <p>We constantly explore new flavors, techniques, and presentations to offer unique and exciting dessert experiences.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-value-card">
          <h3>Community</h3>
          <p>We believe in giving back to our community and creating a welcoming environment for all our customers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-section fade-in">
      <h2 class="about-heading">Our Team</h2>
      <p class="about-text">
        Our team consists of skilled pastry chefs, bakers, and dessert enthusiasts who share a passion for creating exceptional sweet treats. Each member brings their unique expertise and creativity to our kitchen, resulting in the diverse and delicious selection we offer.
      </p>
      <p class="about-text">
        We take pride in our work and are committed to providing not only outstanding desserts but also excellent customer service. Our goal is to make every visit to Sweet Delights a delightful experience.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-section fade-in">
      <h2 class="about-heading">Visit Us</h2>
      <p class="about-text">
        We invite you to visit our bakery and experience our desserts firsthand. Our friendly staff is ready to help you find the perfect treat for any occasion.
      </p>
      <div class="about-visit-card">
        <h3>Store Hours</h3>
        <p><strong>Saturday - Friday:</strong> 7:00 AM - 8:00 PM</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>